<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        header,
        nav,
        footer {
            width: 100%;
            max-width:screen;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
            background: #f0f2f5;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin: 0px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav {
            background: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            width: 100%;
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background: #575757;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            box-sizing: border-box;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 350px;
            /* Set a maximum width */
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .container h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        footer {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: auto;
            max-height: 40px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 10px;
                width: 80%;
            }

            .container h2 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }

            .container p {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }

        
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }
            nav a {
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            footer{
                width: 100%;
            }
            
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Our Company</h1>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="/app/home">Home</a>
        <a href="/app/about">About</a>
        <a href="/app/services">Services</a>
        <a href="/app/contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="/user/Logout">Logout</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to our company! We are dedicated to providing top-notch services and products to our customers. Our
            journey began in 2000, and since then, we have grown into a leading player in the industry.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our mission is to innovate and offer the best solutions to our clients. We believe in quality, integrity,
            and excellence. Our team of experienced professionals works tirelessly to meet and exceed the expectations
            of our customers.
        </p>
        <p>
            We are proud to have a diverse and talented team that brings together a wealth of knowledge and expertise.
            Together, we strive to create a positive impact and contribute to the success of our clients and partners.
        </p>
        <p>
            Thank you for choosing our company. We look forward to serving you and building a long-lasting relationship.
        </p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Our Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>